data.description: Come view this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home conveniently located in the heart of West Monroe.  The kitchen features updated counter tops, back-splash, kitchen sink, a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, built in china cabinet and tile flooring. Newly painted rooms. Beautiful refinished hardwood floors throughout bedrooms and halls.  One bedroom has an en suite bathroom and ornamental ceiling.  There are several unique rooms - one is a loft that could be an artist's dream with natural lighting afforded by three circular windows five feet in diameter.  The home is located on an acre lot for spacious play area or outdoor BBQs on the 30 X 30 paved patio. There is a basketball hoop on the front drive and 3 outbuildings with electricity which could be fashioned into she sheds or man caves!
